{"tid":1306643,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"八達通將可在 iPhone 和 Apple Watch 上使用","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T08:30:32.000Z","uid":4816,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c03647dccb236ef4e5f1779427980427fd35a05d","tid":1306643,"uid":4816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8wVo1Zr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8wVo1Zr.png&h=e979b589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八達通將可在 iPhone 和 Apple Watch 上使用<br />\n（香港，2019年7月11日）八達通卡有限公司一向致力提供創新的支付服務，以配合客戶多元化支付需要，公司宣布今年稍後，客戶將可在 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 上透過 Apple Pay ，使用八達通支付公共交通及零售交易。公司會於稍後公布更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/media/press-releases/2019/20190711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.octopus.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fcorporate%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2F2019%2F20190711.html&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=3750963b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/media/press-releases/2019/20190711.html</a>"},{"pid":"1b85df5db41ce30f4b67d3c50fba8739d18047c1","tid":1306643,"uid":3290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"已經有兩個Post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306632\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306632</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306624\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306624</a>"}]}